'''比尔·博图斯'''（{{lang|en|'''Bill Birtles'''}}）是一名[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]记者，供职于[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳大利亚广播公司]]工作。2015年至2020年在中国工作，在[[成蕾|成蕾]]被拘后，[[澳大利亚驻华大使馆|澳大利亚驻华大使馆]]建议他离开中国返回澳大利亚。

==教育==
博图斯在{{le|堪培拉文法学校|Canberra Grammar School}}读书，2002年后考入[[新南威尔士大学|新南威尔士大学]]<ref name="CGS Alumni">{{cite web |title=Mr Bill Birtles Class of 2002 |url=https://cgsalumni.org.au/profiles/mr-bill-birtles-class-of-2002/ |website=CGS Alumni |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307163440/https://cgsalumni.org.au/profiles/mr-bill-birtles-class-of-2002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==事业==
博图斯最初供职于{{le|Triple J|Triple J}}，担任记者。24岁后他开始学习[[普通话|普通话]]并搬到北京，从事新闻工作。之后他在供职于[[悉尼|悉尼]]、墨尔本的[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳大利亚广播公司]]分部。2015年，他再次搬至北京，担任澳大利亚广播公司驻北京的记者<ref name="CGS Alumni"/>。

2020年8月，随着澳大利亚记者[[成蕾|成蕾]]被捕<ref>{{cite web |last=Birtles |first=Bill |title=Cheng Lei, Australian anchor for China's government-run English news channel CGTN, detained in Beijing |url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-08-31/australian-detained-in-china-television-anchor-cheng-lei/12615362 |website=ABC News |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415005353/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-08-31/australian-detained-in-china-television-anchor-cheng-lei/12615362 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，澳大利亚驻华大使馆建议他离开中国。在他离境前夜，七名中国公安警察访问他家，并禁止他离境；[[澳大利亚金融评论|澳大利亚金融评论]]记者的迈克尔·史密斯（{{lang|en|Michael Smith}}）也经历相同情况。次日，博图斯进入[[澳大利亚驻北京大使馆|澳大利亚驻北京大使馆]]。几天后，博图斯在与中国当局就成蕾一事进行了面谈后，获准离开中国<ref>{{cite web |last1=Doran |first1=Matthew |last2=Dziedzic |first2=Stephen |title=Australian correspondents Bill Birtles and Mike Smith pulled out of China after five-day diplomatic standoff over national security case |url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-09-08/bill-birtles-mike-smith-evacuated-china-safety-concerns/12638786 |website=ABC News |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414231524/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-09-08/bill-birtles-mike-smith-evacuated-china-safety-concerns/12638786 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Davidson |first1=Helen |last2=McGowan |first2=Michael |title=Australia 'very disappointed' after journalists Bill Birtles and Michael Smith forced to flee China |url=https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2020/sep/08/australian-journalists-abc-afr-china-embassy-warnings-bill-birtles-michael-smith |website=The Guardian |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208063714/https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2020/sep/08/australian-journalists-abc-afr-china-embassy-warnings-bill-birtles-michael-smith |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Cave |first1=Damien |last2=Buckley |first2=Chris |title=Fearing Detention, Two Australian Correspondents Flee China |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/07/world/australia/china-correspondents-bill-birtles-michael-smith.html |website=The New York Times |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415031705/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/07/world/australia/china-correspondents-bill-birtles-michael-smith.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Galloway |first1=Anthony |title=Australian journalists Bill Birtles, Mike Smith forced out of China |url=https://www.smh.com.au/politics/federal/australian-journalists-bill-birtles-mike-smith-forced-out-of-china-20200908-p55tg0.html |website=The Sydney Morning Herald |accessdate=24 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318120805/https://www.smh.com.au/politics/federal/australian-journalists-bill-birtles-mike-smith-forced-out-of-china-20200908-p55tg0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=添油加醋！又一个澳大利亚前驻华记者自称曾遭“中方威胁”|url=https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_09_22_565933.shtml?s=sywglbt|accessdate=2021-03-02|work=www.guancha.cn}}</ref>。

2021年3月，[[西九龍裁判法院|香港西九龙裁判法院]]审理此因初选违反[[中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法|国安法]]被起诉的47人，大批民众在法院门口支持国安法。博图斯发Twitter撰文称赞反对国安法的示威民众“很勇敢”，但所用截图中的民众却清晰地用中文写着“支持国安法”。事情一经发现，博图斯成为各国舆论和民众的笑柄<ref>{{Cite web|title=澳媒记者想借这张图抹黑香港国安法，场面十分尴尬|url=https://news.163.com/21/0301/18/G41B94FH00018AP1.html|accessdate=2021-03-02|date=2021-03-01|last=网易|work=news.163.com|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301155023/https://news.163.com/21/0301/18/G41B94FH00018AP1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=自称被中国“调查”跑路的澳媒记者又借香港作妖，这次栽了大跟头|url=https://china.huanqiu.com/article/428JU4t5UMj|accessdate=2021-03-02|work=环球网}}</ref>。
